---
title: Rich Spiced Beef Arrabiata with cheese and chilli flakes
description: A simple and super speedy pasta dish. Red wine jus adds depth and richness to the lightly spiced sauce that coats the juicy beef strips in this Italian-inspired recipe. Perfect for days when you want something that's flavourful, filling, and ready in a flash.
